  "detailed_description": "Harvest hustlers is a chaotic couch co-op farming game for one to four players. Working as a team, you and your fellow farmers must grow vegetables, feed animals, cook and serve orders the demanding farmers market visitors before they leave in anger!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farming with friends</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/ee2d22196f5d9aed2eb890181d6714b5.poster.avif?t=1723707314\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/ee2d22196f5d9aed2eb890181d6714b5.webm?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/ee2d22196f5d9aed2eb890181d6714b5.mp4?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play 1-4 players and work as a team!<br></li><li> Cooperate to get orders out and serve orders!<br></li><li> Watch out, this game can break-up friendships and couples!</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harvest all summer long</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/1c48d78b97a224377879d6e723eb3c5f.poster.avif?t=1723707314\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/1c48d78b97a224377879d6e723eb3c5f.webm?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/1c48d78b97a224377879d6e723eb3c5f.mp4?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Plant, grow and harvest different vegetables!<br></li><li> See veggies grow and harvest them before they go bad!<br></li><li> Nurture plants with water, sun and love</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take care of animals</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/8bd459fc949925eea2e356ebdda73a92.poster.avif?t=1723707314\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/8bd459fc949925eea2e356ebdda73a92.webm?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/8bd459fc949925eea2e356ebdda73a92.mp4?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Take care of cows, chickens and pigs!<br></li><li> Feed them to get animal products and make them happy!<br></li><li> Watch out, all animals move around and ain't afraid to get in your way!</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cook with machines!</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/3b174a8c431dc271057fea7c42e09744.poster.avif?t=1723707314\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/3b174a8c431dc271057fea7c42e09744.webm?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/3b174a8c431dc271057fea7c42e09744.mp4?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make many different recipes!<br></li><li> Cooperate to deliver as many orders as possible!<br></li><li> Watch out, everything which cooks can burn!</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose between many characters!</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/6d65f7dd0e5d6c4b126e2dbc4af1f332.poster.avif?t=1723707314\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/6d65f7dd0e5d6c4b126e2dbc4af1f332.webm?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934630/extras/6d65f7dd0e5d6c4b126e2dbc4af1f332.mp4?t=1723707314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Inclusive farming characters so you can express yourself!<br></li><li> Diverse characters, choose between different skin colours, religions and genders!<br></li><li> Lot's of female farmers!</li></ul>",
